MY CYBERSECURITY JOURNEY

#This repository is a documentation of my Cybersecurity Journey.
Hi, I’m Damilola.
I’m transitioning from a background in sales and banking into the world of technology and Cybersecurity. This journey is a bold step for me because I’m starting from scratch, learning new skills, challenging myself daily, and pushing beyond my comfort zone to build a future in tech.

Dammy_toCyber

What Dammy_toCyber really means to me is my entire transition journey from working in sales and banking to building a future in tech through Cybersecurity. It represents growth, consistency, discipline, resilience, and the courage to start over in a completely different field.

Why Cybersecurity?

I chose Cybersecurity because technology is becoming a major part of our everyday lives, and with that comes the increasing need to protect people, businesses, systems, and data from cyber threats. Cybersecurity stood out to me because it combines problem-solving, continuous learning, critical thinking, and real-world impact.

I also love the fact that Cybersecurity is a field where learning never stops. Every day comes with new challenges, new threats, and new opportunities to grow. For me, this journey is not just about getting into tech — it is about building a meaningful career, creating opportunities for myself, and proving that it is never too late to start again.


